  "description": "<p>We are looking for a Chef who is responsible for developing recipes, planning menus, and managing food\npreparation, ensuring each dish meets both taste and presentation expectations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Menu Planning</li><li>Recipe Development</li><li>Food Preparation and Presentation</li><li>Inventory and Cost Control</li><li>Training and Monitoring Staff</li><li>Health and Safety Compliance</li><li>Quality Control</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in Kitchen environment</li><li>Strong Leadership Skills</li><li>Creativity and Attention to Detail</li><li>Excellent Time Management</li><li>Knowledge of Food Safety and Sanitation Standards:</li><li>Budgeting</li><li>Physical Stamina</li></ul>",
